{"tid":648206,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（長文慎入）既然咁多人反保險，覺得保險佬食水深，有冇人材可以攪間保險公司出黎？","createTime":"2018-04-30T13:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T13:19:40.000Z","uid":182067,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32c104ef68cfe6b2c3212ce5d4a50c109f278320","tid":648206,"uid":182067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"有讀過risk management 都明白，知道保險係一個工具去減低自身既風險。當然每個人既情況都唔同，需求都唔一樣。<br />\n<br />\n大前提，無哂所有agent 同commission 既開支，保費會唔會有得平？就我而言，最有可能用到下面呢3個：<br />\n<br />\n1. 人壽<br />\n買黎卑親人。當你有兩三個小朋友，都靠哂你開飯，我覺得可以買10/20年terms insurance，最低價錢，保到最多（理論，但我發覺間間都唔同$，相差都幾大）<br />\n<br />\n2. 危疾<br />\n買黎自救。間間賠既定義都唔一樣。我最後買左一間（聲稱）最易有得賠。。。感覺都係伏伏地。<br />\n<br />\n3. 醫療<br />\n公司有，自已無諗過買。。。<br />\n<br />\n其實政府有冇機會整番間保險公司，專係做人壽/危疾/醫療？（全民醫保？）唔使sales, commission 又唔使出，自己入哂資料，計出黎應該最平啦，個pool 又大。<br />\n(一定有人話會官相勾結，貪污呢的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者有冇白武士整番間保險公司，等我地唔使卑agent 食多層？感覺上良好的。事實係可能pool唔夠大，卑既保費仲貴過其他有agent既保險公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果保險公司個pool 50%盈富基金加公用股，30%買物業收租，10%做小型貸款，10%成立天使基金，呢個組合，諗起都high high 地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自high <br />\n<br />\n保險公司要求：-<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ia.org.hk/tc/supervision/reg_insurers_lloyd/regulatory_requirements.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ia.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fsupervision%2Freg_insurers_lloyd%2Fregulatory_requirements.html&d=sa8YgtJdsX6r1gXYSKZ%2FfaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=5dadef19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ia.org.hk/tc/supervision/reg_insurers_lloyd/regulatory_requirements.html</a><br />\n<br />\n揾班有經驗（又上哂岸）既人攪番間，眾籌開保險公司有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屬唔屬於非法集資？"},{"pid":"8c2c07990cbdf401cd8df5dfc6daeaef7940aba8","tid":648206,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:11:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e64bf81c5aec9fe0aef1a029d614aa23e8b5eda5","tid":648206,"uid":130033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"有經驗（又上哂岸）既人只會想搵更多commission, 睬你都傻"},{"pid":"385a14ae57dc0753558f3c08d529bdf567e5a38a","tid":648206,"uid":182067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e64bf81c5aec9fe0aef1a029d614aa23e8b5eda5","tid":648206,"uid":130033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"有經驗（又上哂岸）既人只會想搵更多commission, 睬你都傻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"Sad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598ef8dec48337723c339224d96815bb43285490","tid":648206,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"所有法例都係保障有錢佬、大財團<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}